# Full Paths

When describing files and scripts, always use **full paths** (absolute or workspace-relative from project root), not just filenames.

## Examples

- ✅ `d:\rust\ember\client\src\lib.rs`
- ✅ `d:\rust\ember\server\src\main.rs`
- ✅ `d:\rust\ember\build-android.ps1`
- ❌ `lib.rs`
- ❌ `main.rs`
- ❌ `build-android.ps1`

## Scripts

When mentioning PowerShell scripts or other executable scripts, include the full path:
- `d:\rust\ember\build-android.ps1`
- `d:\rust\ember\sign-apk.ps1`
- `d:\rust\ember\release-android.ps1`
